<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248868>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Spermophora falcata sp. nov., male holotype. A – B. Pedipalpus (A. Prolateral view; B. Retrolateral view); C – D. Distal part of procursus (C. Prolateral view; D. Retrolateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248868/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248869>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Spermophora falcata sp. nov., male holotype (C) and female paratype (A – B, D – E). A. Epigynum, ventral view; B. Vulva, dorsal view; C – E. Habitus (C – D. Dorsal view; E. Ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248869/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248870>
    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Spermophora falcata sp. nov., male holotype (A – C) and female paratype (D – E). A – B. Pedipalpus (A. Prolateral view; B. Retrolateral view); C. Chelicerae, frontal view; D. Epigynum, ventral view; E. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248871>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Known distribution of new species of Pholcidae from Laos. 1. Belisana champasakensis sp. nov.; 2. B. crystallina sp. nov.; 3. B. gigantea sp. nov.; 4. B. khanensis sp. nov.; 5. B. lancea sp. nov.; 6. B. martensi sp. nov.; 7. B. tadetuensis sp. nov.; 8. B. xiangensis sp. nov.; 9. Calapnita longa sp. nov.; 10. Khorata circularis sp. nov.; 11. K. dupla sp. nov.; 12. Pholcus arcuatilis sp. nov.; 13. P. sublaksao sp. nov.; 14. Spermophora falcata sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248871/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

